Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.95,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121538,125959}Maya was chosen by Tsukikage Theatre\Nto play Midori in "Growing Up",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:09.29,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125959,129296}the main role in a competition\Nthat will decide the theatre's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.29,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:129296,132299}But after seeing\NHimekawa Ayumi act as Midori,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.01,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132299,135010}she became disheartened\Nand unable to play the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:135010,140140}Frustrated, Miss Tsukikage threw Maya\Ninto the shed on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:27.14,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141099,147147}{\an5\pos(766,710)\fscy95\blur1\fad(800,0)}—Episode 05—\NTwo Midoris
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149900,153153}Don't even try to attend practice\Nuntil the district contest is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153153,154655}Until then,\Nthink about what you have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159409,160786}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160786,164122}I can't act as good as Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164122,167125}There's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167125,169419}There's too much difference between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169419,172255}I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174383,175467}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177052,180639}I want to go back to Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187062,189356}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189356,191817}You're only a small timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.19,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:191817,195195}The next day,\Nthey started training without Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:19.36,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:195195,199366}Shocked, Maya was left by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:36.59,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:212462,216591}Trapped in the dark cottage,\Nanother night came and passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244745,246580}They're still practicing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:40.23,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274858,280238}Hey, let's do something fun\Nat this celebration on the 20th!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.69,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280238,282699}Yeah, Midori, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282699,284034}Great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284034,285827}What would you all like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285827,287954}Let's make it something we can all enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287954,291583}Don't worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291583,293502}I'll pay for it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297130,300759}The words… are so different\Nfrom how they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303386,305430}Make the role…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305430,306973}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306973,310644}I tried so hard to become Midori,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310644,313730}I forgot to make the role mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318777,320487}I'll throw out everything and try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325700,326952}That's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326952,328203}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328203,331122}Get whatever you want.\NWould you like a ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331122,334584}Or should we get all our toys\Nfrom the Fude store?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336461,340006}You don't have to be shy, Shōta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340507,341591}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341591,344052}Say something, Shōta.\NSay something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344052,346054}Say—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356106,359609}That's right. I was…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.73,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359609,362737}Maya, you don't have to\Nplay Midori anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366032,367158}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367158,369286}Even if I can't be on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369286,372122}acting is all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375917,377836}Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379337,381047}Shōta, don't be so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381047,384134}Hey, Shōta, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384134,385343}Say something—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385343,387304}I'm not being shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387304,390015}Don't tease me like this, Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391600,392392}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392392,394811}Let's continue, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394811,396021}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396021,397606}Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397606,398565}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398565,400233}Let's continue practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400233,403403}You're starting to find your own Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403403,406239}My own… Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406239,409743}Yes. You have to make\NMidori reflect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409743,411620}Make Midori… reflect myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411620,412746}Exactly, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412746,415248}Forget everything about Ayumi's Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415248,417375}Her Midori is her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417375,421838}When you wear Midori's mask,\Nit must be one you created yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421838,423131}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423131,424633}I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424633,425884}I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425884,431097}Maya, no matter how hard it gets,\Ndropping a role is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431097,433934}This is the true hardship of being an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442525,445737}Teacher must have trapped\NMaya in that cottage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445737,448657}in order to force her to face herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448657,451451}But in the middle of a cold snowy night…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451451,456456}Maya and Teacher scare me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456456,459668}Yes, of course, because Shōta\Nis a year younger than you, Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461628,463254}Change the way you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465382,467509}No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468593,469844}Keep it down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472138,473098}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473098,475100}That laugh will fit the scene well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476476,477894}Okay, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478478,481022}See, you get upset so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481022,484275}Maya, change the way\Nyou say it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484275,486277}See, you get upset so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486277,488571}Softer, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488571,491074}See, you get upset so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491074,493034}Hmm. Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493034,495620}See, you get upset so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495620,498039}No, the one before was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498039,499749}Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499749,502669}See, you get upset so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502669,505255}Okay, next scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505255,507298}Mr. Nobu, wipe off the mud with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507298,508883}Softer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509551,512053}Mr. Nobu, wipe off the mud with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512053,514055}Don't forget to hesitate, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515515,517267}Try one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517267,518810}Mr. Nobu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518810,520979}Wipe off the mud with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520979,522814}Say it like you are a little bit shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522814,525025}What's wrong?\NAre you too tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525025,525984}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.15,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:529738,532157}Miss Tsukikage's special training continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:58.32,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:532157,538329}To the onlookers though, what they did\Nseemed more like a battle, not like training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:03.04,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:538329,543043}After five long days,\Ntheir battle finally reached an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546337,548214}Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548214,549549}You're finally getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549549,550884}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556431,558141}What happened, Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558141,559976}Nothing, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559976,562395}Just some narcissuses on the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563605,565231}It's been five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565231,568276}They're finally at the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568276,571196}Who, I wonder, who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572572,575116}Why is it so familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575116,577535}Why is it so dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577535,579704}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579704,582082}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582457,586002}Midori… looks at the narcissuses…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586002,588755}And the curtain closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588755,589839}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589839,591883}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591883,595512}Finally, a new Midori is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597305,598223}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598848,601518}She's passed out.\NCall the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604312,605146}What about Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608483,610110}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610110,612028}Look at that girl, she's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613571,617200}Being free from that training\Nmust make her relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621204,624124}The Association has just sent out\Nthe program for the contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624124,626417}We perform on the same day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626417,627919}as Ondine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627919,630380}And on the last day of the contest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630380,634134}Doing the same play\Nas Ondine is hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634134,636553}but now we have to perform\Nright after them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638763,643977}Our actors have so much skill and talent,\Nthere's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643977,646688}The last day's going to be very entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:649232,651151}Japan National Acting Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656447,658992}Hey, hey. Isn't that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658992,663329}That's Kitajima Maya, the main actor for\NTsukikage Theatre's production of "Growing Up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663329,664122}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664122,666082}Wait, stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666082,667375}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667375,670253}I was so excited to see\NHimekawa Ayumi's rival…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670253,672797}but what a big disappointment.\NShe's just a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673923,675175}Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675633,676551}Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677594,678970}We got some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682515,684350}A purple rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:35.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:691191,695153}I will be watching you.\NYour secret admirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692108,694360}He's here…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694360,696821}Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696821,699115}He's here to see me.
Comment: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:49.70,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:709709,709709}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:53.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:713713,713713}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:56.67,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:716674,716674}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726935,728186}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729812,733650}Ah, Maya, my fellow Midori.\NI am so excited to act alongside you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739197,740573}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742951,743660}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:33.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749582,753253}How can she smile like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753253,756506}Am I really that insignificant to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759592,760593}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761928,763179}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763805,765473}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765473,766683}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768017,770019}Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774440,775775}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777652,779112}How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:03.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779112,783533}I was worried he'd treat me coldly\Nbecause of the rivalry between our theatres…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783533,785785}Let's do our best, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787787,793209}In just a moment, Ondine Theatre\Nwill perform "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.33,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:796879,798339}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807265,809350}Come, let's see how Ondine does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809350,810643}Shall we, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810643,813021}No, I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816566,819068}Ayumi's Midori is hers and only hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819068,821446}I have to focus on becoming my Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822697,824407}Watch closely, Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825283,828328}I will show you every ounce of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830163,833833}Finally, you will see\Nhow futile it is to challenge me.
Comment: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:00.25,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:837795,840256}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843426,844469}Midori…
Comment: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.47,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:844469,845470}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850600,851893}What a pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851893,853019}She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853019,856189}It's okay. Get whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856189,859025}I'll pay for it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860360,862362}It's like we're watching\Na beautiful flower bloom…
Comment: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.61,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:864614,865615}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864906,865740}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865740,868743}Himekawa Utako's daughter is performing\Nevery bit as well as we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868743,870995}The play just began,\Nbut I'm already entranced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870995,872955}Mr. Nobu. Wipe off the mud with this—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872955,876125}I wonder if she would become Nobu's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876125,878211}No more!\NNo more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879295,880463}Oh, Mr. Nobu…!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.00,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:881339,884008}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881672,884384}It's like the original story\Nhas come to life in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884384,886010}See, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886010,887678}We have Shinyo on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889180,890056}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890056,893309}I cannot even bear\Nto see their dirty faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894977,896312}No, not for me!
Comment: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:912912,915373}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923005,924841}What a strong impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924841,929303}Listen to the audience.\NThe play is only halfway done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934475,936436}I hope you understand, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936436,938563}You have to win this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938563,941190}And win the National Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941190,944902}If you fail, Tsukikage Theatre\Nwill go out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950241,953369}Mr. Purple Rose, please watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:59.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955705,959625}I will play my Midori so well\Nthat you won't be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969719,972096}Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972096,973306}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977768,980438}The judges were all very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980438,983274}Your portrayal of Midori\Neven outdid the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984984,986527}Hey, Masumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986527,989447}We've pretty much won already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991991,993034}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993034,994619}Ah, it's Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994619,998581}I'm so happy that our theatres have\Nthe opportunity to compete fairly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998581,999665}Compete fairly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000958,1005505}Choosing the same play,\Ninterfering with our rehearsal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005505,1008090}putting our performance\Nright after Ondine's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008090,1011052}You have used every cheap trick you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011052,1012053}Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012053,1012929}Come, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020520,1021562}Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023606,1026025}Well, at least try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032740,1033366}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037203,1039247}It must be hard to perform\Nafter Himekawa Ayumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040039,1041249}but do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043709,1046712}So that's why you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049840,1052343}It won't work though,\NI'm not scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052343,1054637}I have to do this for my fans, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055388,1056973}Your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056973,1058724}I only have one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058724,1062311}but for his sake, I will do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076242,1078035}I want a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078035,1079495}A ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079495,1083624}My heartbeat's so loud…\NI've got to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084500,1087044}Teacher, Maya's so nervous she's trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087044,1088421}Is she gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090298,1091090}Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091090,1092300}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092300,1094218}You are only a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094218,1095469}Shut up, you're just a bamboo stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:16.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096178,1096929}I'm up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113154,1114822}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114822,1117074}It's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117074,1118534}No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121370,1122538}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130963,1133591}That sounds like fun.
Comment: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.42,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1134508,1135426}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133591,1136927}You'll definitely be able\Nto make everyone laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136927,1139388}Serious looks on the audience's faces…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139388,1140431}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144894,1146729}How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146729,1148439}Hey, that's what Midori says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148439,1149565}Let's do it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149565,1152318}You'd do anything to please her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152318,1153819}You must be in love with Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153819,1155946}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155946,1158324}Now now, don't be shy, Shōta.
Comment: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:29.33,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1164372,1169335}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164789,1169543}Well, this Midori is very… cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169543,1171462}Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171462,1172922}What a terrible Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172922,1175257}She's running around all over the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175257,1177802}Her acting isn't sexy at all,\Nshe's almost a tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177802,1179512}A terrible Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:44.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179512,1184100}They might keep saying that,\Nbut they all can't stop watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184100,1185309}Why?
Comment: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.74,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1204912,1207748}Judging Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204995,1209250}This portrayal is very unorthodox,\Nbut I almost find it refreshing…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212169,1215172}This Midori may be nothing like the original,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215172,1217883}but there's a lot to like\Nabout her interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:01.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258466,1261886}Did you see me, Mr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266432,1270269}We will now announce the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270269,1273606}The winning group will be moving on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273606,1277234}to the National Contest as\Nthe Tōkyō district representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277234,1278569}Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280446,1284158}Third place, Kōno Theatre\Nfor "The Rose Tribe".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286368,1290539}Second place, Kattsu Theatre\Nfor "The Planet of Silk".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292291,1294418}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294418,1295920}First place goes to…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302259,1305054}Ondine Theatre for "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:22:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316065,1321028}But, this year, there will be\Nanother first place group…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321028,1323447}Tsukikage Theatre for "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331247,1334959}Since their scores are tied, the judges\Ndecided to have them share first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338712,1342383}Both groups, please send your representatives\Nto receive your prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:30.26,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1347429,1350266}For Kitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:34.81,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1350266,1354812}this was the start of an endless war\Nbetween these immensely talented women,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:38.89,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1354812,1358899}a clash between new and old\Nthat would become legendary.
